                                                required

  SPOUSAL_CONSENT_RECV          BOOLEAN         Whether spousal consent form has
                                                been received

  IRREVOCABILITY_ACK_TS         TIMESTAMP       When member acknowledged
                                                irrevocable elections

  APP_DEATH_BENEFIT_AMT         DECIMAL(10,2)   Calculated lump-sum death benefit
                                                amount

